measurements.description: Approximately two thousand eight hundred seventy-five flowers and 345 buds on 23 arching inflorescences up to 50cm distributed completely around plant; plant pristine, diameter 150cm, height above pot 90cm, circumference 500cm, grown in bark in a 40-cm diameter plastic pot; sepals and petals semi-porrect, ivory; lip ivory spotted dark purple, keels yellow; anther cap ivory; substance average; texture matte.
